<h1 id="1-在namecheap上设置为"><a href="#1-在namecheap上设置为" class="headerlink" title="1.在namecheap上设置为"></a>1.在<a href="https://www.namecheap.com/" target="_blank" rel="external">namecheap</a>上设置为</h1><table>
